PrecisRe-appointment of RICHARD ALAN STAINSBY, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of three years; and designation of RICHARD ALAN STAINSBY as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), effective June 1, 1998.
